quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  39,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  39,1,is kitaab ka utaara jana khuday-e ghalib ( aur ) hikmat walay ki taraf se hai
  39,2,( ae paighambar ) hum ne yeh kitaab tumhari taraf sachaai ke sath nazil ki hai to khuda ki ibadat karo ( yani ) is ki ibadat ko ( shirk se ) khalis karkay
  39,3,dekho khalis ibadat khuda hi ke liye ( zaiba hai ) aur jin logon ne is ke siwa aur dost banaye hain. ( woh kehte hain ke ) hum un ko is liye pujte hain ke hum ko khuda ka Maqarrab bnadin. to jin baton mein yeh ikhtilaaf karte hain khuda un mein un ka faisla kardey ga. be shak khuda is shakhs ko jo jhoota nashukara hai hadaayat nahi deta
  39,4,agar khuda kisi ko apna beta banana chahta to apni makhlooq mein se jis ko chahta intikhab karleta. woh pak hai wohi to khuda yaktaa ( aur ) ghalib hai
  39,5,isi ne asmano aur zameen ko tadbeer ke sath pedakiya hai. ( aur ) wohi raat ko din par lapaitta hai aur din ko raat par lapaitta hai aur isi ne Sooraj aur chaand ko bas mein kar rakha hai. sab aik waqt muqarrar taq chaltay rahen ge. dekho wohi ghalib ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  39,6,isi ne tum ko 1 shakhs se pedakiya phir is se is ka jora banaya aur isi ne tumahray liye chaar payon mein se aath jore banaye. wohi tum ko tumhari maaon ke pait mein ( pehlay ) aik terhan phir doosri terhan teen andheron mein banata hai. yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai isi ki badshahi hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kahan phiray jatay ho ?
  39,7,agar nashukri karo ge to khuda tum se be parwa hai. aur woh apne bundon ke liye nashukri pasand nahi karta aur agar shukar karo ge to woh is ko tumahray liye pasand kere ga. aur koi uthany wala dosray ka boojh nahi uthaye ga. phir tum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lootna hai. phir jo kuch tum karte rahay woh tum ko betaye ga. woh to dilon ki posheeda baton taq se aagah hai
  39,8,aur jab ensaan ko takleef pahunchti hai to apne perwar-digaar ko pukaarta ( aur ) is ki taraf dil se rujoo karta hai. phir jab woh is ko apni taraf se koi Nemat deta hai to jis kaam ke liye pehlay is ko pukaarta hai usay bhool jata hai aur khuda ka shareek bananay lagta hai taakay ( logon ko ) is ke raste se gumraah kere. keh do ke ( ae kafir Nemat ) apni nashukri se thora sa faida uthalay. phir too to dozakhiyon mein hoga
  39,9,( bhala mushriq acha hai ) ya woh jo raat ke waqton mein zameen par peshani rakh kar aur kharray ho kar ibadat karta aur akhirat se darta aur apne perwar-digaar ki rehmat ki umeed rakhta hai. kaho bhala jo log ilm rakhtay hain aur jo nahi rakhtay dono barabar ho saktay hain? ( aur ) nasiyaat to wohi pakarte hain jo aqalmand hain
  39,10,keh do ke ae mere Bandoo jo imaan laaye ho apne perwar-digaar se daro. jinhon ne is duniya mein neki ki un ke liye bhalai hai. aur khuda ki zameen kushadah hai. jo sabr karne walay hain un ko be shumaar sawab miley ga
  39,11,keh do ke mujh se irshad howa hai ke khuda ki ibadat ko khalis karkay is ki bandagi karoon
  39,12,aur yeh bhi irshad howa hai ke mein sab se awwal musalman banon
  39,13,keh do ke agar mein apne perwar-digaar ka hukum nah manoo to mujhe barray din ke azaab se dar lagta hai
  39,14,keh do ke mein apne deen ko ( shirk se ) khalis karkay is ki ibadat karta hon
  39,15,to tum is ke siwa jis ki chaho parastish karo. keh do ke nuqsaan uthany walay wohi log hain jinhon ne qayamat ke din apne aap ko aur apne ghar walon ko nuqsaan mein dala. dekho yahi Sarih nuqsaan hai
  39,16,un ke oopar to aag ke saibaan hon ge aur neechay ( is ke ) farsh hon ge. yeh woh ( azaab ) hai jis se khuda apne bundon ko darata hai. to ae mere Bandoo mujh se drtay raho
  39,17,aur jinhon ne is se ijtinabkiya ke buton ko poojain aur khuda ki taraf rujookiya un ke liye basharat hai. to mere bundon ko basharat suna do
  39,18,jo baat ko suntay aur achi baton ki pairwi karte hain. yahi woh log hain jin ko khuda ne hadaayat di aur yahi aqal walay hain
  39,19,bhala jis shakhs par azaab ka hukum sadir hochuka. tokiya tum ( aisay ) dozakhi ko mukhlasi day sakuu ge ?
  39,20,lekin jo log apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ke liye ounchay ounchay mehal hain jin ke oopar baala khanaay banay hue hain. ( aur ) un ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain. ( yeh ) khuda ka wada hai. khuda waday ke khilaaf nahi karta
  39,21,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda aasman se pani nazil karta phir is ko zameen mein chashmay bana kar jari karta phir is se khaiti ugata hai jis ke terhan terhan ke rang hotay hain. phir woh khushk hojati hai to tum is ko dekhte ho ( ke ) zard ( hogayi hai ) phir usay choora choora kar deta hai. be shak is mein aqal walon ke liye nasiyaat hai
  39,22,bhala jis shakhs ka seenah khuda ne islam ke liye khol diya ho aur woh apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se roshni par ho ( tokiya woh sakht dil kafir ki terhan ho sakta hai ) pas un par afsos hai jin ke dil khuda ki yaad se sakht ho rahay hain. aur yahi log Sarih gumraahi mein hain
  39,23,khuda ne nihayat achi baatein nazil farmai hain ( yani ) kitaab ( jis ki ayatain baahum ) millti jalti ( hain ) aur duhrai jati ( hain ) jo log apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ke badan ke ( is se ) rongte kharray ho jatay hain. phir un ke badan aur dil naram ( ho kar ) khuda ki yaad ki taraf ( mutwajjah ) ho jatay hain. yahi khuda ki hadaayat hai woh is se jis ko chahta hai hadaayat deta hai. aur jis ko khuda gumraah kere is ko koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi
  39,24,bhala jo shakhs qayamat ke din apne munh se buray azaab ko rokta ho (kiya woh waisa ho sakta hai jo chain mein ho ) aur zaalmon se kaha jaye ga ke jo kuch tum karte rahay they is ke mazay chako
  39,25,jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne bhi takzieeb ki thi to un par azaab aisi jagah se agaya ke un ko khabar hi nah thi
  39,26,phir un ko khuda ne duniya ki zindagi mein ruswai ka maza chakkha diya. aur akhirat ka azaab to bohat bara hai. kash yeh samajh rakhtay
  39,27,aur hum ne logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye is quran mein har terhan ki misalein bayan ki hain taakay woh nasiyaat pakren
  39,28,yeh ) quran arabi ( hai ) jis mein koi aib ( aur ikhtilaaf ) nahi taakay woh dar manen
  39,29,khuda aik misaal bayan karta hai ke 1 shakhs hai jis mein kayi ( aadmi ) shareek hain. ( mukhtalif ul mizaj aur ) badkhu aur aik aadmi khaas aik shakhs ka ( ghulam ) hai. bhala dono ki haalat barabar hai. ( nahi ) ا Alhamdu lillaa balkay yeh aksar log nahi jantay
  39,30,( ae paighambar ) tum bhi mar jao ge aur yeh bhi mar jayen ge
  39,31,phir tum sab qayamat ke din apne perwar-digaar ke samnay chugro ge ( aur jhagra Faisal kardiya jaye ga )
  39,32,to is se barh kar zalim kon jo khuda par jhoot bolay aur sachhi baat jab is ke paas poanch jaye to usay jhutlaye .kiya jahannum mein kafiroon ka thikana nahi hai ?
  39,33,aur jo shakhs sachhi baat le kar aaya aur jis ne is ki tasdeeq ki wohi log mut-taqi hain
  39,34,woh jo chahain ge un ke liye un ke perwar-digaar ke paas ( mojood ) hai. naiko karon ka yahi badla hai
  39,35,taakay khuda un se buraiyon ko jo unhon ne kee daur kardey aur naik kamon ka jo woh karte rahay un ko badla day
  39,36,kiya khuda apne bundon ko kaafi nahi. aur yeh tum ko un logon se jo is ke siwa hain ( yani ghair khuda se ) darate hain. aur jis ko khuda gumraah kere usay koi hadaayat dainay wala nahi
  39,37,aur jis ko khuda hadaayat day is ko koi gumraah karne wala nahi.kiya khuda ghalib ( aur ) badla lainay wala nahi hai ?
  39,38,aur agar tum un se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ko kis ne pedakiya to keh den ke khuda ne. kaho ke bhala dekho to jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho. agar khuda mujh ko koi takleef p_hnchani chahay tokiya woh is takleef ko daur kar saktay hain ya agar mujh par meharbani karna chahay to woh is ki meharbani ko rok satke hain? keh do ke mujhe khuda hi kaafi hai. bharosa rakhnay walay isi par bharosa rakhtay hain
  39,39,keh do ke ae qoum tum apni jagah amal kiye jao mein ( apni jagah ) amal kiye jata hon. anqareeb tum ko maloom hojaye ga
  39,40,ke kis par azaab aata hai jo usay ruswa kere ga. aur kis par hamesha ka azaab nazil hota hai
  39,41,hum ne tum par kitaab logon ( ki hadaayat ) ke liye sachaai ke sath nazil ki hai. to jo shakhs hadaayat paata hai to apne ( bhallay ke ) liye aur jo gumraah hota hai gumraahi se to apna hi nuqsaan karta hai. aur ( ae paighambar ) tum un ke zimma daar nahi ho
  39,42,khuda logon ke marnay ke waqt un ki roohein qabz karleta hai aur jo marey nahi ( un ki roohein ) sotay mein ( qabz karleta hai ) phir jin par mout ka hukum kar chukta hai un ko rok rakhta hai aur baqi roohon ko aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye chore deta hai. jo log fikar karte hain un ke liye is mein nishanain hain
  39,43,kiya unhon ne khuda ke siwa aur safarishi bnalye hain. kaho ke khuwa woh kisi cheez ka bhi ikhtiyar nah rakhtay hon aur nah ( kuch ) samajte hi hon
  39,44,keh do ke sifarish to sab khuda hi ke ikhtiyar mein hai. isi ke liye asmano aur zameen ki badshahat hai. phir tum isi ki taraf lout kar jao ge
  39,45,aur jab tanha khuda ka zikarkiya jata hai to jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay un ke dil منقبض ho jatay hain. aur jab is ke siwa ouron ka zikarkiya jata hai to khush ho jatay hain
  39,46,kaho ke ae khuda ( ae ) asmano aur zameen ke peda karne walay ( aur ) posheeda aur zahir ke jan-nay walay to hi apne bundon mein un baton ka jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain faisla kere ga
  39,47,aur agar zaalmon ke paas woh sab ( maal o mata'a) ho jo zameen mein hai aur is ke sath isi qader aur ho to qayamat ke roz buray azaab ( se mukhlasi panay ) ke badlay mein day den. aur un par khuda ki taraf se woh amar zahir hojaye ga jis ka un ko khayaal bhi nah tha
  39,48,aur un ke aamaal ki buraiyan un par zahir ho jaien gi aur jis ( azaab ) ki woh hansi uratye they woh un ko aaghire ga
  39,49,jab ensaan ko takleef pahunchti hai to hamein pukarnay lagta hai. phir jab hum is ko apni taraf se Nemat bkhshte hain to kehta hai ke yeh to mujhe ( mere ) ilm (o danish ) ke sabab mili hai. ( nahi ) balkay woh azmaish hai magar un mein se aksar nahi jantay
  39,50,jo log un se pehlay they woh bhi yahi kaha karte they to jo kuch wohkiya karte they un ke kuch bhi kaam nah aaya
  39,51,un par un ke aamaal ke wabaal par gay. aur jo log un mein se zulm karte rahay hain un par un ke amlon ke wabaal anqareeb parrin ge. aur woh ( khuda ko ) aajiz nahi kar saktay
  39,52,kiya un ko maloom nahi ke khuda hi jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq ko farakh kardaita hai aur ( jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kar deta hai. jo log imaan laatay hain un ke liye is mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  39,53,( ae paighambar meri taraf se logon ko ) keh do ke ae mere Bandoo jinhon ne apni jaanun par zayad-ti ki hai khuda ki rehmat se na umeed nah hona. khuda to sab gunaaho ko bakhash deta hai. ( aur ) woh to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  39,54,"aur is se pehlay ke tum par azaab aa waqay ho, apne perwar-digaar ki taraf rujoo karo aur is ke farmanbardar hojao phir tum ko madad nahi miley gi"
  39,55,aur is se pehlay ke tum par nagahan azaab aajay aur tum ko khabar bhi nah ho is nihayat achi ( kitaab ) ki jo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tum par nazil hui hai pairwi karo
  39,56,ke ( mbada is waqt ) koi mutnaqas kehnay lagey ke ( haae haae ) is taqseer par afsos hai jo mein ne khuda ke haq mein ki aur mein to hansi hi karta raha
  39,57,ya yeh kehnay lagey ke agar khuda mujh ko hadaayat deta to mein bhi parhaiz garon mein hota
  39,58,ya jab azaab dekh le to kehnay lagey ke agar mujhe phir aik dafaa duniya mein jana ho to mein naiko karon mein ho jaoon
  39,59,( khuda farmaiye ga ) kyun nahi meri ayatain tairay paas poanch gayi hain magar to ne un ko jhtlaya aur shekhi mein agaya aur to kafir ban gaya
  39,60,aur jin logon ne khuda par jhoot bola tum qayamat ke din dekho ge ke un ke munh kalay ho rahay hon ge.kiya ghuroor karne walon ko thikana dozakh mein nahi hai
  39,61,aur jo parhaizgaar hain un ki ( Saadat aur ) kamyabi ke sabab khuda un ko nijaat day ga nah to un ko koi sakhti puhanche gi aur nah ghumnaak hon ge
  39,62,khuda hi har cheez ka peda karne wala hai. aur wohi har cheez ka nigaran hai
  39,63,isi ke paas asmano aur zameen ki knjyan hain. aur jinhon ne khuda ki aayton se kufarkiya wohi nuqsaan uthanay walay hain
  39,64,keh do ke ae naadano! tum mujh se yeh kehte ho ke mein ghair khuda ki parastish karne lagun
  39,65,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tumhari taraf aur un ( payghambaroon ) ki taraf jo tum se pehlay ho chukay hain yahi wahi bhaije gayi hai. ke agar tum ne shirkkiya to tumahray amal barbaad ho jaien ge aur tum zayan karon mein hojao ge
  39,66,balkay khuda hi ki ibadat karo aur shukar guzaron mein ho
  39,67,aur unhon ne khuda ki qader shanasi jaisi karni chahiye thi nahi ki. aur qayamat ke din tamam zameen is ki muthi mein hogi aur aasman is ke dahinay haath mein liptay hon ge. ( aur ) woh un logon ke shirk se pak aur aliiiii shaan hai
  39,68,aur jab sor phonka jaye ga to jo log aasman mein hain aur jo zameen mein hain sab be hosh ho kar gir parrin ge magar woh jis ko khuda chahay. phir doosri dafaa phonka jaye ga to foran sab kharray ho kar dekhnay lagen ge
  39,69,aur zameen apne perwar-digaar ke noor se jagmaga uthay gi aur ( aamaal ki ) kitaab ( khol kar ) rakh di jaye gi aur paighambar aur ( aur ) gawah haazir kiye jayen ge aur un mein insaaf ke sath faislakiya jaye ga aur be insafi nahi ki jaye gi
  39,70,aur jis shakhs ne jo amalkiya hoga is ko is ka poora poora badla mil jaye ga aur jo kuch yeh karte hain is ko sab ki khabar hai
  39,71,aur kafiroon ko giroh giroh bana kar jahannum ki taraf le jayen ge. yahan taq ke jab woh is ke paas poanch jayen ge to is ke darwazay khol diye jayen ge to is ke Darogha un se kahin ge kekiya tumahray paas tum hi mein se paighambar nahi aeye they jo tum ko tumahray perwar-digaar ki ayatain parh parh kar sunaate aur is din ke paish anay se darate they kahin ge kyun nahi lekin kafiroon ke haq mein azaab ka hukum mutahaqqiq hochuka tha
  39,72,kaha jaye ga ke dozakh ke darwazon mein daakhil hojao hamesha is mein raho ge. taqqabur karne walon ka bura thikana hai
  39,73,aur jo log apne perwar-digaar se drtay hain un ko giroh giroh bana kar bahisht ki taraf le jayen ge yahan taq ke jab is ke paas poanch jayen ge aur is ke darwazay khol diye jayen ge to is ke Darogha un se kahin ke tum par salam tum bohat achay rahay. ab is mein hamesha ke liye daakhil hojao
  39,74,woh kahin ge ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne apne wada ko hum se sacha kardiya aur hum ko is zameen ka waris bana diya hum bahisht mein jis makaan mein chahain rahen to ( achay ) amal karne walon ka badla bhi kaisa khoob hai
  39,75,tum firshton ko dekho ge ke arsh ke gird ghaira bandhay hue hain ( aur ) apne perwar-digaar ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh kar rahay hain. aur un mein insaaf ke sath faislakiya jaye ga aur kaha jaye ga ke har terhan ki tareef khuda hi ko sazawar hai jo saaray Jahan ka maalik hai
